      <title>Baillie 淡化科技股，转而青睐“乏味”的基础设施股</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/baillie-cools-on-tech-in-favor-of-boring-infrastructure-stocks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Baillie Gifford &amp; Co. 以投资高增长科技股而闻名，现在它看好“乏味的”美国基础设施公司，因为在经历了多年的投资不足之后，它看到了建设热潮。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-10/baillie-cools-on-tech-in-favor-of-boring-infrastructure-stocks</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Dec 2024 06:02:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
